    <div class="row">

  <div class="col-md-2">
<h4 id="sectionTitle">
<font color="#4CAF50">Short Bio</font>
</h4>
</div>

<div class="col-sm-9" id="shortBio">
<div class="span">
<p align="justify"> I am a Ph.D. candidate in the Department of Computer Science & Engineering at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln. The overarching theme of my research is the design and performance analysis of data centers. My current research focuses on the design of free space optical data center architectures utilizing the high capacity and high speed of free space optical technology. I am also working on the design of a novel class of 2D free space optical multicast-capable switch using tri-state switching element. </p>

  </div>
  </div>
  </div>



  <hr>

