<h4 id="sectionTitle">
<font color="#4CAF50">Recent News</font>
</h4>
</div>

<div class="col-sm-9" id="recentNews">
<div class="span">
<ul>

<li>
<div align="justify"><b><font color="#0000FF">[PAPER]</font></b> <strong>June 16, 2016:</strong> Our paper "OWCell: Optical Wireless Cellular Data Center Network Architecture" has been accepted by IEEE International Conference on Communications (ICC).</div>
</li>


<li>
  <div align="justify"><b><font color="#0000FF">[PAPER]</font></b> <strong>June 16, 2016:</strong> Our paper "A New Class of Rearrangeable Non-Blocking Multicast Free Space Optical Switches" has been accepted by IEEE/OSA Journal of Optical Communications and Networking (JOCN).</div>
</li>
<li>
  <div align="justify"><b><font color="#0000FF">[PAPER]</font></b> <strong>March 10, 2016:</strong> Our paper "Low-Complexity Energy-Efficient Spectrum Allocation Algorithm for Cognitive Radio Networks" has been accepted by International Conference on Informatics and Systems (INFOS 2016).</div>
</li>
<li>
  <div align="justify"><b><font color="#0000FF">[PAPER]</font></b> <strong>January 29, 2016:</strong> Our paper "Optical Wireless Communications for Airport Surface Operations: Opportunities and Challenges" has been accepted by 2016 Integrated Communications, Navigation, and Surveillance (ICNS) Conference.</div>
</li>

</ul>

